wikipedia_page.main: Philip Anthony Taylor (born 11 July 1958) is an English former professional footballer who played as a winger in the Football League for York City and Darlington, in non-League football for Woodland Rangers and Guisborough Town and was on the books of Lincoln City without making a league appearance.
